<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4536936>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 16. A median joining network of Chaoborus flavicans (Meigen) sequences from the barcoding region of mitochondrial DNA. 93 sequences were used and the pie diameters are proportional to the number of individuals detected per haplotype. Hash marks on the network represent substitutions and the smallest black circles represent unobserved haplotypes. Colors indicate one of three major geographic regions." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4536936/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4536920>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 9. Pupal respiratory organs. Chaoborus flavicans (Meigen), a) slender type from a pond population (Finland, Urjala), b) voluminous type from a lake population (Canada, Ontario, Kenora), c) C. albipes (Finland, Savonlinna), d) C. posio Salmela sp. n. (Finland, Posio)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4536920/files/figure.png" .

